screen_desc: The screenshot shows a mobile app interface with the title "Confirm your information" at the top. Below the title, there are input fields for "First Name" and "Last Name" with the values "Ethan" and "Do" respectively. There is also a field for a mobile number prefixed with the country code "+84" and a flag icon representing Vietnam. At the bottom, there are navigation buttons: a left arrow for going back and a "Next" button for proceeding. The time displayed at the top of the screen is 10:58 AM, and various status icons are visible.
